pipeline.name: TIKA IMAGE DETECTION WITH DERIVATIVE MEDIA TESSERACT OCR (WITH EAST REGIONS) AND KEYWORD TAGGING AND MARKUP PIPELINE
pipeline.description: Performs Tika image detection followed by Tika text detection on source media. Performs Tesseract OCR and markup on feed-forward regions from EAST on derivative media. Keyword tagging is performed on all TEXT results.

actions.name: TIKA IMAGE DETECTION ACTION
actions.description: Executes the Tika image detection algorithm using the default parameters.

tasks.name: TIKA TEXT DETECTION SOURCE MEDIA ONLY TASK
tasks.description: Performs Tika text detection on source media only, no derivatives.

actions.name: TIKA TEXT DETECTION SOURCE MEDIA ONLY ACTION
actions.description: Executes the Tika text detection algorithm using the default parameters on source media only, no derivatives.

tasks.name: EAST TEXT DETECTION DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY TASK
tasks.description: Runs EAST text detection on derivative media only.

actions.name: EAST TEXT DETECTION DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY ACTION
actions.description: Runs EAST text detection on derivative media only.

tasks.name: TESSERACT OCR TEXT DETECTION (WITH FF REGION) DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY TASK
tasks.description: Performs Tesseract OCR on feed-forward regions on derivative media only.

actions.name: TESSERACT OCR TEXT DETECTION (WITH FF REGION) DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY ACTION
actions.description: Performs Tesseract OCR on feed-forward regions on derivative media only.

tasks.name: KEYWORD TAGGING (WITH FF REGION) TASK
tasks.description: Performs keyword tagging on feed-forward tracks and detections.

actions.name: KEYWORD TAGGING (WITH FF REGION) ACTION
actions.description: Performs keyword tagging on feed-forward tracks and detections.

tasks.name: OCV GENERIC MARKUP DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY TASK
tasks.description: Performs object markup in images and videos for derivative media only.

actions.name: OCV GENERIC MARKUP DERIVATIVE MEDIA ONLY ACTION
actions.description: Performs object markup in images and videos for derivative media only.
